eding to have selected the right tool; what it does do is make the choice m=
ore apparent to the user at a more appropriate stage in the process, and th=
at=E2=80=99s no small thing. I also suspect that GPTs will be much faster t=
han plug-ins, given they are integrated from the get-go. Finally, standalon=
e GPTs are a much better fit with the store model that OpenAI is trying to =
develop.

Still, there is a better way: Altman demoed it.

ChatGPT and the Universal Interface
-----------------------------------

Before Altman introduced the aforementioned GPTs he talked about improvemen=
ts to ChatGPT:

